title: Fargo
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Beer/Wine, European, Spanish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Self-described as modern European cuisine, slow food restaurant, opened Oct 2014. Offers a weekly changing menu according to the seasons and the market with usually a vegan main dish choice. Extensive alcohol menu. Bright space with minimal decor, a lounge room with sofas and free Wi-Fi.
